  "raw_html": "<main class=\"bd-main\" id=\"main-content\" role=\"main\">\n<div class=\"bd-content\">\n<div class=\"bd-article-container\">\n<div class=\"bd-header-article d-print-none\">\n<div class=\"header-article-items header-article__inner\">\n<div class=\"header-article-items__start\">\n<div class=\"header-article-item\">\n<nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"d-print-none\">\n<ul class=\"bd-breadcrumbs\">\n<li class=\"breadcrumb-item breadcrumb-home\">\n<a aria-label=\"Home\" class=\"nav-link\" href=\"../index.html\">\n<i class=\"fa-solid fa-home\"></i>\n</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"breadcrumb-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"../pytorch-api.html\">Reference API</a></li>\n<li class=\"breadcrumb-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"../torch.html\">torch</a></li>\n<li aria-current=\"page\" class=\"breadcrumb-item active\">torch.outer</li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"header-article-items__end\">\n<div class=\"header-article-item\">\n<div class=\"rating\">\n    Rate this Page\n    <div class=\"stars\">\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"1\" data-value=\"1\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"2\" data-value=\"2\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"3\" data-value=\"3\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"4\" data-value=\"4\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"5\" data-value=\"5\">★</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"searchbox\"></div>\n<article class=\"bd-article\" id=\"pytorch-article\">\n<!-- Hidden breadcrumb schema for SEO only -->\n<div itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/BreadcrumbList\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<div itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ListItem\">\n<link href=\"../pytorch-api.html\" itemprop=\"item\"/>\n<meta content=\"Reference API\" itemprop=\"name\"/>\n<meta content=\"1\" itemprop=\"position\"/>\n</div>\n<div itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ListItem\">\n<link href=\"../torch.html\" itemprop=\"item\"/>\n<meta content=\"torch\" itemprop=\"name\"/>\n<meta content=\"2\" itemprop=\"position\"/>\n</div>\n<div itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ListItem\">\n<meta content=\"torch.outer\" itemprop=\"name\"/>\n<meta content=\"3\" itemprop=\"position\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"searchbox\"></div>\n<article class=\"bd-article\">\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"torch-outer\">\n<h1>torch.outer<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#torch-outer\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\">#</a></h1>\n<dl class=\"py function\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\" id=\"torch.outer\">\n<span class=\"sig-prename descclassname\"><span class=\"pre\">torch.</span></span><span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">outer</span></span><span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span><em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">input</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">vec2</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">*</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">out</span></span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">None</span></span></em><span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span> <span class=\"sig-return\"><span class=\"sig-return-icon\">→</span> <span class=\"sig-return-typehint\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../tensors.html#torch.Tensor\" title=\"torch.Tensor\"><span class=\"pre\">Tensor</span></a></span></span><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#torch.outer\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">#</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Outer product of <code class=\"xref py py-attr docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">input</span></code> and <code class=\"xref py py-attr docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">vec2</span></code>.\nIf <code class=\"xref py py-attr docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">input</span></code> is a vector of size <span class=\"math\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"katex-html\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span></span> and <code class=\"xref py py-attr docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">vec2</span></code> is a vector of\nsize <span class=\"math\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>m</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">m</annotation></semantics></math></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"katex-html\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">m</span></span></span></span></span>, then <code class=\"xref py py-attr docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">out</span></code> must be a matrix of size <span class=\"math\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>×</mo><mi>m</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">(n \\times m)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"katex-html\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">×</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">m</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span>.</p>\n<div class=\"admonition note\">\n<p class=\"admonition-title\">Note</p>\n<p>This function does not <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../notes/broadcasting.html#broadcasting-semantics\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">broadcast</span></a>.</p>\n</div>\n<dl class=\"field-list simple\">\n<dt class=\"field-odd\">Parameters</dt>\n<dd class=\"field-odd\"><ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p><strong>input</strong> (<a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../tensors.html#torch.Tensor\" title=\"torch.Tensor\"><em>Tensor</em></a>) – 1-D input vector</p></li>\n<li><p><strong>vec2</strong> (<a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../tensors.html#torch.Tensor\" title=\"torch.Tensor\"><em>Tensor</em></a>) – 1-D input vector</p></li>\n</ul>\n</dd>\n<dt class=\"field-even\">Keyword Arguments</dt>\n<dd class=\"field-even\"><p><strong>out</strong> (<a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../tensors.html#torch.Tensor\" title=\"torch.Tensor\"><em>Tensor</em></a><em>, </em><em>optional</em>) – optional output matrix</p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<p>Example:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-default notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">v1</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">torch</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">arange</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"mf\">1.</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mf\">5.</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">v2</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">torch</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">arange</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"mf\">1.</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mf\">4.</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">torch</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">outer</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">v1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">v2</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"go\">tensor([[  1.,   2.,   3.],</span>\n<span class=\"go\">        [  2.,   4.,   6.],</span>\n<span class=\"go\">        [  3.,   6.,   9.],</span>\n<span class=\"go\">        [  4.,   8.,  12.]])</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</dd></dl>\n</div>\n</article>\n</article>\n<footer class=\"bd-footer-article\">\n<div class=\"footer-article-items footer-article__inner\">\n<div class=\"footer-article-item\">\n<div class=\"feedback\">\n<div class=\"rating\">\n    Rate this Page\n    <div class=\"stars\">\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"1\" data-value=\"1\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"2\" data-value=\"2\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"3\" data-value=\"3\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"4\" data-value=\"4\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"5\" data-value=\"5\">★</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedback-send\">\n<button class=\"feedback-btn\" data-bs-placement=\"bottom\" data-bs-title=\"Create a GitHub Issue\" data-bs-toggle=\"tooltip\" data-gtm=\"feedback-btn-click\" onclick=\"openGitHubIssue()\">Send Feedback\n    </button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"prev-next-area\">\n<a class=\"left-prev\" href=\"torch.ormqr.html\" title=\"previous page\">\n<i class=\"fa-solid fa-angle-left\"></i>\n<div class=\"prev-next-info\">\n<p class=\"prev-next-subtitle\">previous</p>\n<p class=\"prev-next-title\">torch.ormqr</p>\n</div>\n</a>\n<a class=\"right-next\" href=\"torch.pinverse.html\" title=\"next page\">\n<div class=\"prev-next-info\">\n<p class=\"prev-next-subtitle\">next</p>\n<p class=\"prev-next-title\">